    "a83c7fb5-a342-4a07-83d9-c0de76bb58fb": {
      "type": "section-richtext",
      "settings": {
        "kicker": "Wella Professionals",
        "title": "Color Fresh Mask",
        "text": "<p><strong>Refresh your salon color.</strong></p><p>The Color Fresh Mask is the perfect combination of temporary color and complete care; a treatment that revives and refreshes your hair color, while keeping strands silky-smooth and moisturized. If you’re looking for a way to boost salon color between pro appointments, this is your go-to, allowing you to get a speedy refresh at home.</p>",
